divs: Sighting DetailsWe were driving and noticed initially...what we thought a really strange bright v shaped cloud on horizon. As we got closer we notice it was an odd shaped craft going from left to right across the horizon. As we came up on it, the craft went straight up out of view quickly and disappeared. Feelings were none...just curious like what is that
